name: Geomantic omen
description: Expend time, mana, etc. to find secret places on various maps.
description_schinese: 寻找秘境。

name: Lost cave mansion
description: This is a mysterious mystic realm space, vast inside, containing various treasures. Here you can find various items such as elixirs, magical treasures, cultivation techniques, minerals, etc.
description_schinese: 这是一个神秘的秘境空间，内部广阔，藏有各种宝物。在这里，你可以找到丹药、功法、矿物等各种物品。

name: Hidden mineral veins
description: This mystic realm is filled with various rare minerals, where you can mine a large amount of ores.
description_schinese: 这个秘境中充满了各种珍稀矿物，在这里，你可以开采到大量的矿石。

name: Withered herb garden
description: This is an already withered apothecary garden. There may still be some plant seeds here. You can find various kinds of herbal medicine, fruit trees, flowers, and other plant seeds here.
description_schinese: 这个已经枯萎的药园。可能还有一些植物的种子。在这里你可以找到各种各种草药、果树、花卉等植物的种子。

name: Secret herb garden
description: This is a medicinal garden that grows various rare fruits. Here you can find all kinds of rare fruits, etc.
description_schinese: 这是一个生长有各种珍稀果实的药园。在这里你可以找到各种珍稀的果实等。

name: Abandoned elixir room
description: This is an abandoned alchemy room, containing various precious alchemy resources. Here you can find various rare medicinal herbs and elixirs, etc.
description_schinese: 这是早已荒废的炼丹房，藏有各种珍贵的炼丹资源。在这里你可以找到各种珍稀药材和丹药等。

name: Shennong Mystic Realm
description: This is a mystic realm that contains various precious planting formulas and special soil. Here you can find secret recipes that record how to cultivate rare plants and improve crop yields.
description_schinese: 这是一个藏有各种珍贵的种植秘方和特殊土壤的秘境。在这里你可以找到记录着如何培育珍稀植物、提高作物产量等高级种植技艺的秘方。

name: Hidden alchemy room
description: This is an alchemy room that treasures various precious alchemy formulas and precious magical treasures. Here you can find alchemy secret recipes that record how to refine various elixirs and improve alchemy success rates.
description_schinese: 这是一个珍藏有各种珍贵的炼丹配方的炼丹房。在这里你可以找到记录着如何炼制各种丹药、提高炼丹成功率等炼丹技巧的炼丹秘方。

name: Hidden weapon workshop
description: This is a weapon workshop that treasures various precious forging formulas and precious magical treasures. Here you can find forging secret recipes that record how to create various weapons and armor and improve forging success rates.
description_schinese: 这是一个藏有各种珍贵的炼器配方和珍贵法宝的炼器坊。在这里你可以找到记录着如何打造各种武器和护甲、提高炼器成功率等炼器技巧的炼器秘方。

name: Hidden sutra library
description: This is a sutra library that treasures various precious cultivation techniques and insights. Here you can find cultivation techniques that record how to improve one's修为 and break through bottlenecks.
description_schinese: 这是一个藏有各种珍贵的修炼功法和心得的藏经阁。在这里你可以找到记录着如何提升自己的修为、突破瓶颈的修炼功法。
